{"tid":1663640,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"十三萬連署籲美出兵救香港 白宮須回應","createTime":"2019-10-19T14:02:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-20T01:40:06.000Z","uid":184679,"like":394,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"65eb63f549a5d48ec56840a49550ca0d24a876bb","tid":1663640,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:02:15.000Z","msg":"香港「反送中」運動持續至今，光是官方公布的數據，就有超過兩千五百人遭到逮捕。署名「A.H.」的民眾在白宮請願網站「We the People」發起請願，請美國派出武力，救援在香港受到警方以近距離射擊、瞄準頭部等方式，遭到暴力鎮壓的手無寸鐵的民眾。有超過十三萬人連署支持，依照規定一個月內超過十萬的連署，白宮都必須正式做出回應。另外美國共和黨參議員盧比歐表示，希望《香港人權與民主法案》，能盡快在下週，在參議院進行表決。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20191019/video/256237.html?十三萬連署籲美出兵救香港%20白宮須回應\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ntdtv.com.tw%2Fb5%2F20191019%2Fvideo%2F256237.html%3F%E5%8D%81%E4%B8%89%E8%90%AC%E9%80%A3%E7%BD%B2%E7%B1%B2%E7%BE%8E%E5%87%BA%E5%85%B5%E6%95%91%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%2520%E7%99%BD%E5%AE%AE%E9%A0%88%E5%9B%9E%E6%87%89&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=72955a5b\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.ntdtv.com.tw/b5/20191019/video/256237.html?十三萬連署籲美出兵救香港%20白宮須回應</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nPlease send US Armed force to Hong Kong to rescue citizens from the massacre carried out by the Hong Kong Police Force.<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fplease-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force&d=om99xhx1cOxPLv9Q%2FbR%2FoB1%2FCJV8QLW4B9aSVLpa5FM%3D&h=120e01a6\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/please-send-us-armed-force-hong-kong-rescue-citizens-massacre-carried-out-hong-kong-police-force</a>"},{"pid":"794a4a83ed446853245b6ecec843575433cd5c2a","tid":1663640,"uid":47605,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-19T14:02:34.000Z